des:
Ambience of a beautiful interior design with video on Echo Spot and Echo Show and audio on any regular Echo devices. 

Get a breathtaking audiovisual experience on your Echo device. Optimized for Echo Show and Echo Spot, this skill does not only provide ambient sounds but enriches the experience with high-quality video of a beautiful interior design in a seamless loop.

It can help you fall asleep or gives a calming atmosphere to your home.
Impress your guests with fascinating screensaver on Echo Show and Echo Spot.

Enjoy this and tell us what you feedback and suggestion about this.
